Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,设想一下 你回到过去 在你祖父遇上你祖母之前\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lmagine you go back in time and kill your own grandfather...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将其杀死\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}before he meets your grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.74,0:18:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你就绝不可能再生出来了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Therefore, you never would've been born...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样从一开始 也就不可能回到过去了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and therefore couldn't have gone back in time...in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.46,0:18:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是 循环就成了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And then the loop is set up of...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能 不可能\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}possible, impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生 不会发生\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}happened, it didn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:18:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是马利特认为\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But Mallett believes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理论物理学的最新进展\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}recent advances in theoretical physics...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.51,0:19:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表明这些似是而非根本就不是什么问题\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}suggest that these paradoxes aren't a problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在很多物理学家突发奇想认为\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Many physicists now believe in the far-out notion...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的宇宙只是许多平行宇宙中的一个\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that our universe...is just one of many parallel universes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 当你回到过去时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So that when you go back in time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可能实际上是进入了一个平行宇宙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you might actually be entering a parallel universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.03,0:19:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在其中 你可以改变事件\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in which you can alter events...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不影响你来的那个宇宙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}without affecting the universe you came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.78,0:19:29.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们认为时间长河可能存在着漩涡\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We believe that the river of time can have whirlpools...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你或许能够通过它回到过去\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}whirlpools by which you may be able to go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.42,0:19:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰到你出生以前的父母\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and meet your parents before you're born...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者甚至分叉进入两条河里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or perhaps even fork into two rivers...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你就可以改变过去\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}by which you can actually alter the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.09,0:19:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,创造一个备用的宇宙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to create an alternate universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.13,0:19:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是 如今现代物理学非常前卫的整个理论\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}These are all theories...that are at the very forefront of modern physics today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马利特认为我们或许用不了一个世纪\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mallett believes we may be as little as a century away...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.73,0:19:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类就可以进行时间穿梭了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}from time travel by humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:20:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过他回去救父亲为时已晚了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Still too late for him to travel back in time...to save his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.32,0:20:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 怎么称呼？- 洛基\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- And your name? - Rocky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 幸会 - 谢谢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Nice to meet you. - Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请记得空间发生的事情\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Rememberwhat's happening to space.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它在不停地旋转\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's swirling around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而他的个人损失已经为后人的新天地\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But his personal loss has opened a door...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开了一扇门\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}for a newworld forfuture generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我基于这个基本方程式上发展起来的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}l developed the basic equations for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.46,0:20:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经让我能够与世界分享某些东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt has led to my being able...to share something with the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.05,0:20:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我以前从不能分享到的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that l would never have been able to share before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.31,0:20:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉那其实是对我老爸能够做到的最好的缅怀\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And l feel that,that it's actually...a fitting memorial to my father...that l've been able to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.98,0:20:39.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对此我感觉良好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}l feel very good about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.71,0:21:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于宇宙最早的形成\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As the universe was first forming...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科学家认为\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}scientists believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.47,0:21:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其成分不只是构成我们周围一切的常规物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it was comprised of more thanjust the regular matter...that now makes up everything around us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.89,0:21:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们认为它具有几乎等量的反物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They believe it had...an almost equal amount of anti-matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.56,0:21:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,物质的难以捉摸的邪恶孪生兄弟\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}matter's elusive evil twin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你回到宇宙的最初期\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If you go back to the very early universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果就是它是由物质和反物质构成的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it turns out that it was made of matter and anti-matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.83,0:21:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来每个粒子都有一个反粒子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt turns out that every particle has an anti-particle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.25,0:21:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听上去好像很荒唐但却是真的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And it sounds kind of crazy, but it's real...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.13,0:21:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点科幻 告诉你 反物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and sort of sci-fi, you know, anti-matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.63,0:21:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 神秘的反物质究竟是什么\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But what is this mysterious anti-matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.05,0:21:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又都到哪去了呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and where did all of it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.59,0:21:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反物质其实就像物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Anti-matter is exactly like matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的不同之处实际上在于\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The difference between it is the fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.68,0:21:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它与之关联的电荷完全不同\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that it has a completely different charge...associated with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.15,0:22:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,常规物质的成分是原子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Regular matter is made of atoms...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.19,0:22:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来的成分是次原子粒子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}which in turn are made of subatomic particles...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.90,0:22:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如带负电荷的电子和带正电荷的质子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}like negatively charged electrons...and positively charged protons.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.03,0:22:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反物质是这些粒子的对应面\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Anti-matter are the opposite of these particles.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.91,0:22:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们有相同的质量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They have the same mass...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.08,0:22:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却有着相反的电荷\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but the opposite electrical charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.21,0:22:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,质子是正电荷粒子 是原子核\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Proton's a positively charged particle...that's the nucleus of the atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.50,0:22:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而反质子就是负电荷质子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The anti-proton would be a negatively charged proton...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.76,0:22:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,具有相同的质量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that has exactly the same mass.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.09,0:22:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们的宇宙间 异性相吸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln our universe, opposites attract...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.97,0:22:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粒子和反粒子相互吸引\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and particles and anti-particles are pulled together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.60,0:22:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人会认为这种关系是天合之作\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}One would think this is...a relationship made for the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.36,0:22:46.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而每次物质与反物质打交道时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But every time matter comes in contact with anti-matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.28,0:22:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果无一例外\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the outcome is the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.53,0:22:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们同归于尽\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they annihilate each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.58,0:23:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想象一下空中两架飞机迎面飞翔的情况\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lmagine two spaceships hurtling through space...on a collision course.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.38,0:23:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一架是常规物质做成的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}One is made of regular matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.38,0:23:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一架是外星文明造的反物质飞船\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The other is an anti-matter craft...built by an alien civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.93,0:23:20.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰撞将非常壮观\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The impact would be spectacular...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.52,0:23:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将不会留下任何残骸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and there would be no wreckage left behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.65,0:23:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,供宇宙撞机调查员来审视\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}for cosmic crash investigators to examine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.99,0:23:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,物质与反物质消失殆尽\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The matter and the anti-matter disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.20,0:23:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扑的一下 它们不见了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Poof, they're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.57,0:23:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 能量没有消失\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But the energy doesn't disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.03,0:23:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能量以两种能量非常高的γ射线的形式再现:光子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The energy re-emerges in the form...of two very energetic gamma rays: photons.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.83,0:23:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锁定在很小质量里的能量相当惊人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And the amount of energy...locked up in a tiny amount of mass...is quite astonishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.59,0:23:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你将物质与反物质结合在一块 就会爆炸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lf you take matter and anti-matter...and combine it, it is explosive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.81,0:24:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上 这是宇宙间最大的能源之一:\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And in fact, it is one of the greatest sources...of energy in the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.85,0:24:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,物质与反物质的碰撞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the collision of matter and anti-matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.56,0:24:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我是你的话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So if l were you...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.69,0:24:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不会将反物质放进口袋\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}l would not put anti-matter in your pocket...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.65,0:24:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你知道什么是值得的话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}if you knowwhat's good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.70,0:24:14.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反物质在碰上物质时极易挥发\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Volatile as anti-matter is when it meets matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.61,0:24:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在着巨大的潜能\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}there's a tremendous energy potential...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.74,0:24:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我们知道如何去驾驭它\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ifwe knew how to harness it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.74,0:24:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了得到物质里究竟锁定了多少能量的概念\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So to get an idea...how much energy is locked up in matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.42,0:24:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你能想上片刻\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}if you imagine for a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.67,0:24:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有两堆沙子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that these two piles of sand are...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.67,0:24:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一堆是物质 另一堆是反物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that one is matter and one is anti-matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.92,0:24:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你将它们放在一块\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and you let them come together...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.30,0:24:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们就会湮灭并产生能量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they would annihilate and produce energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.72,0:24:35.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会有多少能量呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}How much energy?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.01,0:24:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,供应整个加州一周的能量就在这两堆沙子里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Enough energy to power all of California for a week...just in those two piles of sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.89,0:24:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,围绕反物质最大的谜团在于\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The biggest mystery surrounding anti-matter is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.07,0:24:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在宇宙早期物质与反物质几乎是等量的话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}if there were nearly equal amounts...of matter and anti-matter in the early universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.03,0:24:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么现在所有的反物质都到哪里去了呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}then where is all the anti-matter now?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.66,0:25:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙最大的谜团之一\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}One of the great mysteries of the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.79,0:25:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我们的邪恶孪生兄弟 反物质究竟怎么啦\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is what happened to our evil twin, anti-matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.34,0:25:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们扫视天堂的角角落落\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Everywhere we look in the heavens...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.59,0:25:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只看到普通物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we see ordinary matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.09,0:25:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有见到反物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We don't see anti-matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.59,0:25:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有少量的反物质存在于银河系中心\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's only a small amount of anti-matter...coming out of the center of the Milky Way galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.93,0:25:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何这个宇宙看上去全市由物质构成的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Why this universe appears to be made entirely of matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.44,0:25:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而没有见到什么反物质 真是一头雾水\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and there isn't much anti-matter to be seen out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.94,0:25:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不认为会一直解释不通\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}l don't think it'll ever be explained anyway...is a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.98,0:25:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 脑子里需要有个说法\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but the mind hunts for an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.70,0:25:42.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一种可能或许就是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}One possibility is that perhaps there was...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.08,0:25:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在宇宙早期物质的比例要稍高于反物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a slightly higher percentage of matter than anti-matter...in the early universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.00,0:25:53.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 当粒子与反粒子在湮灭战里碰撞时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So as the particles and anti-particles collided...in a war of annihilation...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.67,0:25:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小部分物质幸存了下来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that small percentage of matter survived...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.18,0:26:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为了最古老战场上幸存的老兵\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the last living veterans of our most ancient battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.73,0:26:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相对10亿个反质子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}For every billion anti-protons...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.36,0:26:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就需要有十亿零一个质子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you need a billion and one protons.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.61,0:26:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦10亿个都牺牲了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Then the billion all annihilate...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.24,0:26:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就留下了那一个质子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and you're left with that one proton.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.37,0:26:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩余的是我方\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And the leftover is us.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.83,0:26:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都是剩余财产\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We are the residue.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.33,0:26:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都是在物质与反物质碰撞那个瞬间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We are the leftover of this titanic blast of energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.30,0:26:39.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,释放出来的巨大能量爆发的残余\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}released by the collision of matter and anti-matter...at the instant of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.35,0:26:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们最先进的理论尚无法解释\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our most advanced theories cannot explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.85,0:26:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何物质与反物质之间存在着这种不平衡\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}why there was this asymmetry between matter and anti-matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.73,0:26:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 苍天有眼 它存在了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But thank God it exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.44,0:26:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则 我们将不会存在\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Otherwise, we wouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.99,0:27:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过即使物质胜出\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But even though matter prevailed...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.62,0:27:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,构成了我们周遭的万物\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to make up everything we see around us...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.12,0:27:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有没有在遥远的星系或空间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}could there be distant galaxies or regions of space...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.92,0:27:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在着反物质称霸一方的可能性呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}where anti-matter still reigns supreme?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.30,0:27:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能会有整个星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt may be that there are entire galaxies...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.84,0:27:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是由99.9%的反物质构成\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that are just 99.9 percent anti-matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.38,0:27:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我们物质构成的星系一样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}just like this one is matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.47,0:27:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果一个反物质星系撞进物质星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And if an anti-matter galaxy...were to run into a matter galaxy...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.97,0:27:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么它们双双会毁于巨大的闪光和能量中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}then they both would be annihilated...in some stupendous flash of light and power.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.61,0:27:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪的是 科学家已经知道了如何\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As strange as it is...scientists have learned how to create...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.40,0:27:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在实验室加速器里创造微量的医用反物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}minute quantities of anti-matter...in laboratory accelerators for medical purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.70,0:27:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自衰变的放射物质的反物质粒子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Particles of anti-matter...from decaying radioactive material...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.12,0:27:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被注射进人体 进行大脑正电子发射断层扫描(PET 扫描)\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are injected into the body...to create PET scans of the brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.67,0:28:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,许多人没有意识到\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Many people don't realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.84,0:28:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他们去医院进行PET扫描时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that when they go to the hospital...and have a PET scan...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.26,0:28:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己实际上被注射了反物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they're actually being injected...with a source of anti-matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.56,0:28:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,PET中的P代表正电子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The P in PET corresponds to positrons.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.35,0:28:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正电子就是反电子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Positrons are anti-electrons.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.90,0:28:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦它进入到我们想了解的人体某个部位\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And when...and it goes to some part of the body...that we're trying to figure out what's going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.73,0:28:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来正电子会被释放出来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}then when the positron's emitted...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.99,0:28:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它会很快找上电子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it finds an electron very quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.45,0:28:24.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起湮灭\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}annihilates with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.53,0:28:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会有γ射线从体内发出\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the gamma rays come out of the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.62,0:28:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从而被侦察到\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and are detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.45,0:28:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它集中在脑力活跃的部分大脑\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt concentrates in the parts of the brain...where there's mental activity...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.46,0:28:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我们可以检测出正电子辐射\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then we can detect the emission...of positron radiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.71,0:28:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就让脑部扫描\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So this allows brain scans...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.29,0:28:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我们大脑思考的漂亮图像\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to give us gorgeous photographs of the thinking brain...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.59,0:28:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其可能性全靠反物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}made possible by anti-matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.18,0:28:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在反物质帮助解开了人脑秘密的同时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}While anti-matter has helped to unlock...the secrets of the human brain...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.73,0:28:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人脑尚无法解开反物质的全部之谜\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the human brain has yet to unlock...all the secrets of anti-matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.81,0:29:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们确实不知道为何现在的宇宙是物质构成的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We do not knowwhy...the universe is made of matter now...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.82,0:29:06.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我们正朝着解决这个问题迈进\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but we are making progress towards answering that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.36,0:29:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要知道 在小步快跑\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You know, little steps at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.62,0:29:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如同我们永恒变化的宇宙中的许多秘密一样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Like many mysteries in our ever-changing universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.17,0:29:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反物质的真相或许目前仍然属于未解之谜\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the truth about anti-matter may remain for now...in the realm of the unexplained.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.51,0:29:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星与神秘始终如影相随\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mars and mystery have always gone hand in hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.85,0:29:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 这颗红色行星最有趣的秘密\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But the most intriguing mystery of the red planet...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.36,0:29:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在于与外来入侵者毫不相干\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}has nothing to do with alien invaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.70,0:29:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科学证据表明火星曾是颗极像地球的行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Scientific evidence suggests that Mars...was once a more Earth-like planet...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.04,0:30:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,具有维系生命的一个关键元素 水\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}with one of the key elements to support life...water.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.71,0:30:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水曾大量存在于火星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Water existed in abundance on Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.72,0:30:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们发现了古河流的证据\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We find the evidence of old flows.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.10,0:30:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在其大气层里发现了零星的水蒸汽\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We see a little tiny bit 0f water vapor...in the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.60,0:30:22.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星上甚至还存在古河谷和冲积平原模样的特征\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There are even features on Mars...that look like old rivervalleys and flood plains.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.20,0:30:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它曾是颗具有海洋的热带行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt was once a tropical planet with oceans and seas...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.03,0:30:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是已经是山穷水尽\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but all that water disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.83,0:30:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星上的水怎么会通通消失殆尽的呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}How could all the water on Mars have simply vanished?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.46,0:30:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何会不见的呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And why did it disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.54,0:30:47.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些都是科学家孜孜以求之谜\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}These are mysteries...that scientists are struggling to solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.17,0:30:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星漫游者和轨道器收集到的地质证据\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Geologic evidence gathered by the Mars rovers and orbiters...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.26,0:30:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,揭示了在35亿年前\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}suggest that 3.5 billion years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.51,0:30:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星潮湿地表发生了戏剧性改变了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mars' watery surface changed dramatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.73,0:31:02.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去温润的行星变成了干冷之地\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The once-temperate planet became a cold, dry place...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.36,0:31:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水消失了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the watervanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.28,0:31:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过弄清楚了水消失的时间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But figuring out when the water disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.40,0:31:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不会告诉你水去了哪里以及原因\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}doesn't tell you where it went orwhy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.12,0:31:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星上的水消失了很久很久了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The water on Mars was lost...a very, very, very long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.08,0:31:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说是由几十亿年了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and l'm talking billions 0f years.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.04,0:31:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让你了解水去了何处的线索早不存在了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And the clues that would lead you to know...where that waterwent are long gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.47,0:31:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星上一系列事件\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A series of events on Mars...
