Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.87,0:37:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提起宇宙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When it comes to the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.83,0:37:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的认识仅限于我们已经了解的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}what we know is surpassed only by what we have yet to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.00,0:37:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在所有的未解之谜中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And of all the unexplained mysteries...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.34,0:37:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个是最大的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}one remains the greatest of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.85,0:37:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大爆炸之前是个什么情况\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Did anything come before the Big Bang...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.68,0:37:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抑或那个事件真是一切的开端？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}orwas that event truly the beginning of everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.69,0:38:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果真如此 那又是什么点燃了爆炸呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And if it was, what was the spark that lit it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.86,0:38:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是整个科学中最大的谜团\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This is the greatest mystery in all of science.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.28,0:38:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么启动了创世本身的呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What started creation itself?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.16,0:38:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大爆炸理论里头存在着这个巨大的漏洞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Big bang theory has this tremendous hole in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.79,0:38:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们茫然不知\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We are clueless.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.54,0:38:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们茫然不知于是什么将大爆炸付之行动的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We are clueless as to what set the Big Bang into motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.35,0:38:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大爆炸是关于137亿年前宇宙诞生的宇宙论模型\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Big Bang is the cosmological model...for the birth of our universe, 13.7 billion years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.40,0:38:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙中的一切\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Everything in our universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.61,0:38:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都可以追溯到那一刻\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}can be traced back to that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.07,0:38:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起始那一刻似乎存在着这个神秘点\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There seems to be...this mysterious point at the beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.29,0:38:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将其称之为奇点\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and we call it the singularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.00,0:38:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使它很神秘\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But even though it's mysterious...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.91,0:39:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有很多未解之谜牵涉其中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and has many open questions associated with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.21,0:39:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但它仍不失为我们时间表上的良好开端\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it still makes a good starting point...for our timeline.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.63,0:39:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我们的科学仪器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But our scientific instruments are blind and deaf...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.34,0:39:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对大爆炸以前时期一无所知\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to the period before the Big Bang...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.76,0:39:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果真存在过这个时期的话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}if such a period existed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.60,0:39:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇点就像是我们永远无法逾越的界限\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The singularity is like...a horizon that we can never see beyond.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.11,0:39:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为在创世中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Because in the creation...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.32,0:39:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间是伴随空间 物质一起创造出来的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}time was created along with space...and along with matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.07,0:39:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大爆炸就是那种事件\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the Big Bang is just that sort of event.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.71,0:39:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 是不可能知道创世之前的情况的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And therefore, it's impossible to knowwhat happened...before the creation event.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.80,0:39:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 对大爆炸之前情况的揣摩\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Nevertheless, scientific speculation...as to what happened before the Big Bang...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.72,0:39:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的是激发了天文物理学最伟大的思想\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is something that intrigues...the greatest minds in astrophysics.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.32,0:40:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些理论家认为我们的宇宙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Some theorists believe that our universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.65,0:40:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会定期经历一次大爆炸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}experiences Big Bangs at regular intervals.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.66,0:40:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个循环模型认为每万亿年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This cyclic model proposes that every trillion years...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.20,0:40:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会有一次大爆炸 随后宇宙开始膨胀\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}there's a Big Bang afterwhich the universe expands...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.29,0:40:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着又坍缩\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}before again collapsing...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.67,0:40:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为下一次大爆炸创造条件\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}setting the stage for another Big Bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.55,0:40:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些有趣的方法可以\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's interesting ways that can connect...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.84,0:40:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联系上前一个宇宙的故事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}with the story of a previous universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.01,0:40:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们宇宙的结尾可以带来另一个宇宙的开端\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The end of one universe can bring the beginning of another.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.31,0:40:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许从来没有过开端\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Maybe there neverwas a start...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.64,0:40:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它或许是从更早的时刻一直延续着\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that it's somehow been ongoing from an earlier moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.86,0:40:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就没有过什么创世者\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and never had a creator at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.83,0:41:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我们对大爆炸之前的解释有可能\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But we might be closer to an explanation...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.66,0:41:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超过了我们的了解\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of the pre-Big Bang than we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.96,0:41:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依然回荡在宇宙间的大爆炸产生的宇宙回响\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The cosmic reverberations from the Big Bang...that still echo through the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.55,0:41:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上 或许掌握着奇点之前那一刻的答案\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}may actually hold the answer...to the moment before the singularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.34,0:41:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来这些驻波是我们了解当今宇宙的关键\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt turns out these standing waves...are key to how we understand the universe today.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.85,0:41:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一开始 膨胀就给了宇宙一个巨大的冲击\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lnflation gives the universe...one big hit at the beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.64,0:41:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我在这里打击面前的这个罐子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}just like l'm hitting the pot right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.73,0:41:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它产生了驻波\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt forms the standing waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.73,0:41:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以在现在的宇宙辐射中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and we can look for those symmetrical patterns...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.07,0:41:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到这些对称的图案\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in the cosmic radiation today.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.91,0:41:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我们发送卫星 观察辐射\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So we send our satellites out, we observe the radiation...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.24,0:41:43.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,观察对称的驻波\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the symmetrical standing waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.04,0:41:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新一波探测器 重力波探测器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A newwave of detectors, gravity wave detectors...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.76,0:41:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将在下一个十年送往外太空\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}will be launched into outer space...in the next decade.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.26,0:42:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过激光相连\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Connected by laser beams...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.39,0:42:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,创世产生的任何冲击波都会震荡这些激光束\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}any shockwave from the incident of creation...will jiggle these laser beams...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.89,0:42:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我们就能够记录到\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and we'll be able to then record...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.31,0:42:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大爆炸本身所留下的震动\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the vibrations left over from the Big Bang itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.78,0:42:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我坚信我们在未来几十年里能够\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's why l'm confident that we'll be able...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.78,0:42:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不光探测到大爆炸本身\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to probe notjust the Big Bang itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.95,0:42:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至还有大爆炸前期的原因所在\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but even the pre-Big Bang era in the coming decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.41,0:42:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,激光还将探测到\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The lasers will also detect...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.08,0:42:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,膨胀能量的源头\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}sources of inflationary energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.12,0:42:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至还能确定创造大爆炸的机制\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and perhaps determine the mechanism...that created the Big Bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.26,0:42:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们努力解决了这个最大的谜团\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If we struggle to solve the greatest mystery of all...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.60,0:42:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们对真正了解宇宙怎么能不抱希望呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}how can we ever hope to really understand the universe?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.31,0:42:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每当你解决了一个问题\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Wheneveryou get an answer to a question...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.31,0:42:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总会引出更多的问题\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it almost always leads to more questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.32,0:42:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你取得了进展 谜团得以解决\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You make progress and mysteries can get solved...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.44,0:42:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但另一方面总是会有更多的谜团\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but then there'll always be more mysteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.29,0:43:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是宇宙不断尝试了解自我的产物\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We are the result...of the universe attempting to understand itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.33,0:43:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是 我对我们在宇宙中的定位的观点\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's my conception of our place in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.09,0:43:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 这让人很难理解\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And so that makes it difficult to understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.05,0:43:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管如此 还是极有可能的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but nevertheless, it might be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.56,0:43:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙在不断变化之中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The universe is constantly changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.40,0:43:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是规律 物理定律是一成不变的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But the laws, the laws of physics...are immutable.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.15,0:43:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们不会改变\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They don't change...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.86,0:43:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它给了我们摆脱混乱的希望\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and that gives us hope that out of all this chaos...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.41,0:43:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将能够解释\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we'll be able to explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.28,0:43:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是如何从一开始一路走来的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}how it all got here to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.83,0:43:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们永恒变化的宇宙中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln our ever-changing universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.29,0:43:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未解之谜会继续困惑我们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the unexplained mysteries will continue to elude us.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.34,0:44:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们正逼近解开我们的终极之谜\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But we are edging ever closer...to unlocking the ultimate secrets...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.30,0:44:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承前启后 继往开来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the keys to our past and the pathways to ourfuture.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.56,0:44:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然 科学已经搞明白了很多东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}While science has made sense of many things...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.85,0:44:13.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 还有大量有待认识的东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}there is still plenty left to be discovered...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.31,0:44:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深藏在广袤 幽深 神秘的宇宙间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}about our vast, dark, and mysterious universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.00,0:44:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢观赏\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Thanks For Viewing
